com.whirvis.jraknet

Annotation Type ThreadedListener


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
public @interface ThreadedListener
    Denotes that either a RakNetServerListener or RakNetClientListener wishes to have its' event methods called on their own dedicated thread.
    Since:
    JRakNet v2.11.0
    Author:
    Whirvis T. Wheatley

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element and Description
      java.lang.String name
      Returns the name that will be used for the threaded event method.

    • Element Detail

      • name

        public abstract java.lang.String name
        Returns the name that will be used for the threaded event method.

        By default, this value is simply "Event".

        Returns:
        the name that will be used for the threaded event method.

        "Event"
